metadata.name: Mixed expression
metadata.description:
This project was inspired by emojis😊
we can express our emotions or idea through emojis on social media😍
The main purpose to create this project is to distribute 70% of the profit 🤑 to the poor children👧👦 and  needy people, who don't even have one time a meal for themself
so, we can put a smile on their face😊 and satisfy their hunger😋
